      "value": "<p>Beginning at 3rd level, you can spend 5 chakra to activate your latent <strong>Junsugan</strong> for the next 10 minutes. When you do, you gain 30 feet of Chakra Sight and Darkvision. Additionally, you gain one of the following 3rd level features (<em>Far Sight 1</em>,<em>Distant Vision</em>, <em>Immaterial Sight</em>, <em>Speed Vision</em>). Your selection cannot be changed later.</p>",
